": 885, \"to\": 909}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/Stephanie Lecocq/Reuters \\\"The Paris Mint is in the center of the capital, right in the middle of the Games, and it makes sense that the body that strikes the medals should tell the story of the Olympic medals,\\\" said collection curator Dominique Anterion.\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 1192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 968, \"end\": 978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monnaie_de_Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Mint\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monnaie_de_Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monnaie_de_Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"/Stephanie Lecocq/Reuters\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 961}, {\"ngram\": \"the center\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 994}, {\"ngram\": \"the capital\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1009}, {\"ngram\": \"the middle\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1030}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"sense\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1063}, {\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1077}, {\"ngram\": \"the medals\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1101}, {\"ngram\": \"the story\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1123}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic medals\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1145}, {\"ngram\": \"collection curator Dominique Anterion\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1190}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's based on our collection because notably here we have made a great number of medals, for Paris but also for Athens, so the first modern Olympic Games, in 1896.\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1358, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1288, \"end\": 1293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.928413551826301e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1307, \"end\": 1313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"score\": 0.9995160585972105, \"rank\": 0.0004841752012808169, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our collection\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1223}, {\"ngram\": \"a great number\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1272}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So the logic is there, to tell this story from 1896 to 2024.\\\"\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1420, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the logic\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1371}, {\"ngram\": \"this story\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE Solar cars and tyre dust: Auto's future at Goodwood Festival of Speed Mackerel getting Norwegian fishermen out of deep water The UK village that inspired the Olympic Games The jeweler Chaumet, owned by the French luxury giant LVMH, tapped into the country's history of refinement and haute couture, as the lead designer of the Paris medals.\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1776, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1521, \"end\": 1530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.9979250904875863, \"rank\": 0.001060092097344949, \"text\": \"Norwegian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}, {\"begin\": 1564, \"end\": 1566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999147403323, \"rank\": 5.878624545490573e-08, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1662, \"end\": 1666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.4303671988098294e-15, \"text\": \"LVMH\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LVMH\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://d