eler here in the renowned Vendome Square, with 244 years of history.\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1956, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the oldest jeweler\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1892}, {\"ngram\": \"the renowned Vendome Square\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1928}, {\"ngram\": \"244 years\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1944}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1955}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So it seemed to us clear that it would be Chaumet that would take charge of the medal design.\\\"\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1975, \"to\": 1977}, {\"ngram\": \"Chaumet\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2008}, {\"ngram\": \"charge\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2031}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal design\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On July 24, as part of the build-up to the Games, the host of the 2030 Winter Olympics was announced.\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2156, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 2058, \"to\": 2062}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2074}, {\"ngram\": \"the build-up\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2090}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2103}, {\"ngram\": \"the host\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2113}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2030 Winter Olympics\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Games were conditionally awarded to the French Alps - subject to the IOC receiving a financial guarantee from the government.\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2286, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2230, \"end\": 2233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2326613194620592e-16, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Games\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2166}, {\"ngram\": \"the French Alps\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2212}, {\"ngram\": \"a financial guarantee\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2265}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2285}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it could mean more medals from the Mint.\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2331, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more medals\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"the Mint\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2330}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There would be a certain logic if the Paris Mint were to strike the medals for the 2030 Games,\\\" said Dominic Anterion.\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2452, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2372, \"end\": 2382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monnaie_de_Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Mint\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monnaie_de_Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monnaie_de_Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a certain logic\", \"from\": 2349, \"to\": 2364}, {\"ngram\": \"the medals\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2408}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2030 Games\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2427}, {\"ngram\": \"Dominic Anterion\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Mint previously made the first-ever Winter Olympics medals for Chamonix 1924, and we also made the medals for the 1968 Games in Grenoble.\\\"\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2454, \"end\": 2462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney_Mint\", \"score\": 0.9997040834998486, \"rank\": 0.0002907374410152913, \"text\": \"The Mint\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney_Mint\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney_Mint\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first-ever Winter Olympics medals\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2516}, {\"ngram\": \"Chamonix\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2529}, {\"ngram\": \"the medals\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2563}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1968 Games\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2582}, {\"ngram\": \"Grenoble\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2594}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a lot of history behind the medals - and the Mint, which was founded in the year 864.\", \"from\": 2598, \"to\": 2692, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2607, \"to\": 2612}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 2616, \"to\": 2623}, {\"ngram\": \"the medals\", \"from\": 2631, \"to\": 2641}, {\"ngram\": \"the Mint\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2656}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2687}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there is a modern side as well - the use of recycled metals.\", \"from\": 2694, \"to\": 2758, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a modern side\", \"from\": 2707, \"to\": 2720}, {\"ngram\": \"the use\", \"from\": 2731, \"to\": 2738}, {\"ngram\": \"recycled metals\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2757}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That adds an environmentally-conscious element to the golds, silvers and bronzes being handed out at this year's Summer Games.\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 2886, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an environmentally-conscious element\", \"from\": 2770, \"to\": 2806}, {\"ngram\": \"the golds\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2819}, {\"ngram\": \"silvers\", \"from\": 2821, \"to\": 2828}, {\"ngram\": \"this year's Summer Games\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2885}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe toStoryboard: A weekly newsletterbringing you the best of CGTN every Friday SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7 Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466 SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7 Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2888, \"to\": 3235, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"toStoryboa